		<h3>Challenge #11</h3>
	<h2>More Shapes!</h2>

        <p>In this chalenge you are going to make your robot
          drive in different shapes. But this time you are going to use
	  <Strong>Methods</Strong>!!!
	</p>

	<img src="../robox/media/Methods.PNG"/><br>	
	
        <p>Methods allow you to use a lot of blocks using only one block!
          Remember how you used a <Strong>Repeat</strong> block to make shapes last time?
	Well instead of just using repeat blocks use method blocks too!</p>

	<img src="../robox/media/LottaCode.PNG"/><br>
	
        <p>Methods make the above code able to be done using the blocks below.</p>

	<img src="../robox/media/LessCode.PNG"/><br>

	<p>Below are the Methods used in the code above.</p>
	
	<img src="../robox/media/MethodA.PNG"/><br>

